# ShopifyQL Plugin Settings
#
# store_url:        Your store domain, e.g. my-store.myshopify.com
# access_token:     Admin API token from your Custom App (starts with shpat_)
# output_preference: smart | always-chat | always-save
#                   smart = ≤20 rows in chat, >20 rows saved to file
# output_dir:       Where to save result files (relative to project root)
#
# Run /shopifyql-setup to fill this in interactively.
# Copy this file to .claude/shopifyql.local.md — do NOT commit that file.
